That old dog—

00:01:08.760 --> 00:01:11.199
Hiding a corpse, yet pretending it's supernatural.

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:12.440
What's the real reason?

00:01:16.519 --> 00:01:18.120
Because of Gu Songbai—

00:01:20.360 --> 00:01:21.319
