00:01:36.559 --> 00:01:37.040
Come here.

00:01:38.160 --> 00:01:38.879
Warm your hands.

00:01:46.959 --> 00:01:49.080
I've sent Yiru to find Madam Wu's body.

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:51.879
If Lady Gu was really killed by Gu Songbai—

00:01:51.959 --> 00:01:53.519
She must've been silenced.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:55.839
If we can find her body—

00:01:55.879 --> 00:01:57.680
We'll surely find evidence.

00:02:03.040 --> 00:02:04.319
You little rascal—

00:02:04.639 --> 00:02:06.040
Pretending to be a ghost wore you out yesterday.

00:02:06.160 --> 00:02:07.279
