00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:11.479
He Fuyi, give me another bowl.

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:13.039
No.

00:02:13.039 --> 00:02:14.559
Finish what's in your bowl first.

00:02:19.199 --> 00:02:19.720
By the way—

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:23.080
You collect Spirit Aura—

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:25.440
To light up the Big Dipper Diagram in the Seven Stars Lamp.

00:02:25.720 --> 00:02:27.440
But what's the point of it?

00:02:27.679 --> 00:02:28.720
Didn't you already—

00:02:28.919 --> 00:02:31.000
Activate the Seven Stars Lamp to save yourself?

00:02:31.639 --> 00:02:33.360
Didn't I tell you before?

00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:35.119
Each time the Seven Stars Lamp is lit—

00:02:35.119 --> 00:02:36.839
It only extends life by twelve years.

00:02:37.119 --> 00:02:38.080
So that means—

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:40.279
After twelve years, I still die.

00:02:44.479 --> 00:02:46.520
It's already been ten years.

00:02:47.800 --> 00:02:49.479
Don't worry, Xiao Wuzi.

00:02:49.919 --> 00:02:52.559
Once all seven stars in the lamp are lit—

00:02:52.679 --> 00:02:54.399
Then I'll unleash—

00:02:54.399 --> 00:02:55.880
My true power.

00:03:03.320 --> 00:03:04.119
At that time—

00:03:04.320 --> 00:03:06.720
Maybe I'll regain my original lifespan.

00:03:11.679 --> 00:03:12.440
Rest assured.

00:03:13.119 --> 00:03:15.600
Before I extend my life by lighting the Big Dipper Diagram—

00:03:15.880 --> 00:03:17.639
I won't let anyone take the Seven Stars Lamp.

00:03:17.759 --> 00:03:18.679
Not even the Empress Dowager.

00:03:22.240 --> 00:03:23.199
Here we go again.

00:03:27.720 --> 00:03:29.639
You still haven't answered my question.

00:03:30.720 --> 00:03:32.039
We've met before—

00:03:32.600 --> 00:03:33.279
Right?

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:39.880
Actually, I—

00:03:42.119 --> 00:03:42.720
Careful!

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:06.160
I said we should stay hidden.

00:04:06.600 --> 00:04:08.039
Since he left this—

00:04:08.119 --> 00:04:09.720
It means he lured us here on purpose.

00:04:09.919 --> 00:04:11.160
No need to hide anything.

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:13.240
Kidnapping Aqi—

00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:14.960
It's likely the remnants of Lan Hai Society.

00:04:15.039 --> 00:04:16.359
They're definitely after you.

00:04:16.640 --> 00:04:18.880
We'd better stay cautious.

00:04:19.959 --> 00:04:20.440
This way.

00:04:20.519 --> 00:04:21.040
Where to?

00:04:22.760 --> 00:04:24.040
You said to be careful.

00:04:24.559 --> 00:04:25.720
Jump the wall in the backyard.

00:04:32.239 --> 00:04:32.799
Aqi!

00:04:33.359 --> 00:04:34.119
Are you okay?

00:04:34.359 --> 00:04:36.040
Why did you take so long?

00:04:36.399 --> 00:04:37.119
I'm done eating.

00:04:38.239 --> 00:04:39.440
It's nice here.

00:04:39.799 --> 00:04:42.119
Qin Yu gave me lots of tasty food.

00:05:00.880 --> 00:05:01.559
Stop!

00:05:03.519 --> 00:05:04.519
You're Qin Yu.

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:31.760
Leave no survivors.

00:05:43.040 --> 00:05:43.600
Anyone here?

00:05:46.839 --> 00:05:47.440
No.

00:05:49.839 --> 00:05:51.440
You're with Lan Hai Society.

00:05:56.519 --> 00:05:58.040
Seems you've figured it out.

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:02.119
Circumstances forced my hand.

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:04.600
I had no choice but to do this.

00:06:18.679 --> 00:06:19.679
To lure you here.

00:06:20.040 --> 00:06:21.440
I have something important to tell you.

00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:24.000
But before that—

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:25.839
I have one more question.

00:06:28.640 --> 00:06:29.600
When you entered the city yesterday—

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:31.559
Why did you visit the Gu and Yang residences?

00:06:32.079 --> 00:06:32.760
Investigating a case.

00:06:34.600 --> 00:06:35.279
What case?

00:06:35.519 --> 00:06:38.600
Is Lady Gu's possession case related to you?

00:06:44.359 --> 00:06:45.760
I thought you already knew—

00:06:45.760 --> 00:06:46.600
My identity.

00:06:47.320 --> 00:06:49.920
So you targeted Miss Gu on purpose.

00:06:50.880 --> 00:06:52.320
We really are investigating.

00:06:52.519 --> 00:06:53.640
And we learned—

00:06:53.760 --> 00:06:55.839
About your past with the Gu family fifteen years ago.

00:06:56.279 --> 00:06:57.959
But we never expected—

00:06:58.200 --> 00:06:59.799
You were with Lan Hai Society.

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:02.839
Now you act like you're forced into this.

00:07:03.119 --> 00:07:04.200
What does it mean?

00:07:04.839 --> 00:07:05.720
In recent days—

00:07:06.320 --> 00:07:07.799
Lan Hai Society was suppressed by the court.

00:07:09.160 --> 00:07:11.679
All the contacts in the capital were wiped out.

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:15.200
After Shen Changfeng escaped, he found me.

00:07:15.839 --> 00:07:16.959
He ordered me to—

00:07:19.799 --> 00:07:21.239
Kill this girl, Aqi.

00:07:26.760 --> 00:07:28.279
Now He Fuyi and Prince Bayintu—

00:07:28.279 --> 00:07:29.559
Have entered Shandong.

00:07:30.239 --> 00:07:30.839
If they really—

00:07:30.839 --> 00:07:32.239
Bring the Seven Stars Lamp to the Forbidden City—

00:07:32.519 --> 00:07:34.119
That witch will get what she wants.

00:07:37.440 --> 00:07:38.359
Not to mention He Fuyi—

00:07:38.959 --> 00:07:40.160
Just Prince Bayintu alone—

00:07:40.279 --> 00:07:41.959
They're top experts in the capital.

00:07:42.279 --> 00:07:43.799
Snatching the treasure from them—

00:07:44.119 --> 00:07:45.119
Is nearly impossible.

00:07:45.880 --> 00:07:46.320
Brother Qin—

00:07:47.320 --> 00:07:48.399
No need to seize the treasure.

00:07:49.519 --> 00:07:50.119
You just need to—

00:07:50.119 --> 00:07:51.679
Kill the child with them.

00:07:53.399 --> 00:07:54.160
Child?

00:07:54.440 --> 00:07:54.959
Yes.

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:57.320
Master said—

00:07:58.359 --> 00:07:59.279
Seven Stars Descend upon the Child.

00:08:00.679 --> 00:08:02.799
That kid must be linked to the Seven Stars Lamp.

00:08:03.119 --> 00:08:03.600
Kill her—

00:08:03.600 --> 00:08:04.440
And it's settled for good.

00:08:05.359 --> 00:08:06.640
It's always about the Seven Stars Lamp.

00:08:07.559 --> 00:08:09.119
For this elusive legend—

00:08:09.119 --> 00:08:10.679
Haven't we sacrificed enough?

00:08:11.600 --> 00:08:12.359
Don't forget—

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:14.519
We founded Lan Hai Society for reform.

00:08:14.519 --> 00:08:15.480
For change.

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:17.320
But you focus only on—

00:08:17.320 --> 00:08:18.480
Assassinating the Empress Dowager.

00:08:18.880 --> 00:08:20.480
That's why we've achieved nothing for years.

00:08:20.480 --> 00:08:21.359
All because of that witch.

00:08:21.359 --> 00:08:22.519
The dynasty is rotting.

00:08:22.679 --> 00:08:24.239
Killing her is saving the nation.

00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:26.320
She's dying now.

00:08:26.359 --> 00:08:27.440
She's dying.

00:08:29.079 --> 00:08:31.119
I won't let the Seven Stars Lamp extend her life.

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:34.280
You're obsessed—mad.

00:08:35.400 --> 00:08:36.799
We can't work together if our paths differ.

00:08:37.679 --> 00:08:39.440
I won't be swayed by your words—

00:08:39.679 --> 00:08:41.679
Or do those evil deeds again.

00:08:42.440 --> 00:08:43.200
Stop!

00:08:52.479 --> 00:08:54.080
Since you're so compassionate,

00:08:55.280 --> 00:08:57.719
I suppose you'd even risk that lady's life

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:00.200
and wouldn't hesitate, right?

00:09:02.479 --> 00:09:03.239
You dare?

00:09:10.159 --> 00:09:11.000
Are you going or not?

00:09:11.559 --> 00:09:12.880
Shen Changfeng, to kill the Empress Dowager,

00:09:12.880 --> 00:09:14.799
has become completely obsessed.

00:09:15.239 --> 00:09:16.000
He uses me

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:19.760
and threatens my family's lives

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:21.640
to force me to kill this young girl.

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:22.599
I have no choice.

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:23.760
I had to agree first,

00:09:23.760 --> 00:09:24.679
then figure out a plan later.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:25.799
Family?

00:09:26.599 --> 00:09:27.919
You mean Gu Shuyin, right?

00:09:29.119 --> 00:09:31.479
You've secretly protected Yang Kaizhi for years

00:09:31.679 --> 00:09:32.640
all for her sake.

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:34.840
What really happened fifteen years ago?

00:09:34.880 --> 00:09:36.440
Did you ever consider eloping?

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:38.799
Miss Gu and I—

00:09:40.880 --> 00:09:41.440
No,

00:09:41.679 --> 00:09:43.679
Madam Yang and I never crossed the line.

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:45.479
She once saved my life,

00:09:45.719 --> 00:09:47.520
so I owe her my life in return.

00:09:47.799 --> 00:09:49.880
You make it sound so forced.

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:51.080
But once,

00:09:51.280 --> 00:09:52.599
didn't you willingly join the Lan Hai Society

00:09:52.599 --> 00:09:53.679
and those rebels?

00:09:54.679 --> 00:09:55.679
Rebels?

00:09:57.359 --> 00:09:59.119
If seeking reform for the people

00:09:59.280 --> 00:10:01.520
means we're rebels,

00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:03.039
then people like you,

00:10:03.479 --> 00:10:04.640
who hold empty titles,

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:07.159
ruling others by birth alone,

00:10:07.159 --> 00:10:08.880
always acting superior,

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:10.679
what does that make you?

00:10:10.840 --> 00:10:12.039
By your logic,

00:10:12.640 --> 00:10:15.599
you wise men who worry for the world

00:10:16.119 --> 00:10:18.000
came up with reforms

00:10:18.640 --> 00:10:20.760
that led to slaughtering Zhenhuan Biaoju's people?

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:21.719
I...

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:35.320
You still recognized me.

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:39.200
Your hand is easy to spot.

00:10:42.520 --> 00:10:43.559
All my life,

00:10:44.799 --> 00:10:46.080
because of my low status,

00:10:47.080 --> 00:10:48.159
I've been bullied,

00:10:48.719 --> 00:10:49.799
slandered,

00:10:50.119 --> 00:10:51.080
wrongfully imprisoned,

00:10:51.080 --> 00:10:51.559
and...

00:10:53.840 --> 00:10:55.599
forced to part from my beloved.

00:10:58.280 --> 00:10:59.440
So I swore

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:00.840
to change this world.

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:02.080
I want everyone,

00:11:03.159 --> 00:11:04.359
no matter their status,

00:11:04.359 --> 00:11:05.760
to live with dignity.

00:11:08.640 --> 00:11:09.359
Later,

00:11:10.799 --> 00:11:11.960
I met Master Zhuang

00:11:12.679 --> 00:11:14.039
and joined the reformists.

00:11:15.559 --> 00:11:16.479
But soon after,

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:18.679
the court massacred us.

00:11:20.679 --> 00:11:21.880
After Lan Hai Society was founded,

00:11:23.039 --> 00:11:24.520
we chose to abandon normal methods

00:11:24.520 --> 00:11:25.400
for reform.

00:11:26.799 --> 00:11:28.080
Instead, we used more drastic

00:11:28.719 --> 00:11:30.080
and effective means.

00:11:31.640 --> 00:11:34.200
Assassinating the Empress Dowager—is that your "effective means"?

00:11:34.479 --> 00:11:36.479
With the world in chaos now,

00:11:36.679 --> 00:11:38.359
is it all because of a foolish Empress Dowager?

00:11:42.440 --> 00:11:44.080
At this point, I must admit

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:46.239
Lan Hai Society's path

00:11:46.559 --> 00:11:47.760
has not only narrowed,

00:11:48.679 --> 00:11:49.520
but also gone astray.

00:11:50.280 --> 00:11:51.239
And all of this

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:52.960
started ten years ago,

00:11:54.039 --> 00:11:55.840
because of that Master.

00:11:56.119 --> 00:11:57.000
Which Master?

00:11:57.159 --> 00:11:58.039
Be clear.

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:03.640
I don't know his name.

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:04.760
But it was him

00:12:04.919 --> 00:12:05.799
who brought us the Seven Stars Lamp.

00:12:05.799 --> 00:12:07.559
The news of being taken by imperial guards—

00:12:07.840 --> 00:12:08.599
that was also him.

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:11.280
He incited Shen Changfeng to keep hunting.

00:12:12.479 --> 00:12:14.320
To keep Lan Hai Society hidden,

00:12:16.440 --> 00:12:17.599
he ordered Zhenhuan Biaoju

00:12:19.640 --> 00:12:20.559
to be wiped out.

00:12:21.919 --> 00:12:23.159
Don't think that by blaming everything

00:12:23.200 --> 00:12:24.719
on some unknown Master,

00:12:24.719 --> 00:12:25.679
whose name you don't even know,

00:12:26.239 --> 00:12:28.159
you can wash your hands of the massacre.

00:12:30.159 --> 00:12:31.119
I know.

00:12:34.400 --> 00:12:35.200
It's been ten years.

00:12:36.760 --> 00:12:38.200
I've burned so much paper for the dead,

00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:41.919
but I dream of those souls every night.

00:12:42.039 --> 00:12:43.200
What are his features?

00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:47.080
When did he approach you?

00:12:47.479 --> 00:12:48.400
And when was it?

00:12:54.799 --> 00:12:55.640
It's deadly poison.

00:13:03.159 --> 00:13:04.200
What does he look like?

00:13:04.479 --> 00:13:05.760
What else did he tell you?

00:13:06.440 --> 00:13:07.000
No...

00:13:07.080 --> 00:13:07.960
The poison's too strong.

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:09.080
He won't last long.

00:13:11.679 --> 00:13:12.400
Qin Yu.

00:13:12.880 --> 00:13:13.799
You owe me—

00:13:14.359 --> 00:13:16.080
you owe Zhenhuan Biaoju's lost souls

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:17.000
an explanation.

00:13:17.080 --> 00:13:18.000
Speak.

00:13:18.200 --> 00:13:18.960
Don't faint!

00:13:19.440 --> 00:13:20.239
Miss Gu!

00:13:22.039 --> 00:13:22.840
Miss Gu!

00:13:24.440 --> 00:13:25.640
It's the Seven Stars Dream.

00:13:25.960 --> 00:13:27.679
It's Qin Yu's dying wish.

00:13:28.479 --> 00:13:29.280
Speak!